name: MEC Dateline Passport Wallet
description: Unobtrusive simplicity for your essential travel documents. The low-profile design stows easily in jacket pockets, carry-ons and money belts. Durable water-resistant fabric survives the rigours of cross-continental travel.Polyester with water-resistant coating.RFID shield layer between lining and outer fabric prevents information theft.4 internal slots for cards and a sleeve for your airline tickets or documents.Passport sleeve fit the cover of a bulky 10-year Canadian passport (slide the back cover in the sleeve, so you can flash it at the gate).
